  "title": "Education Sales Manager (PEI Recruitment)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Identify, develop, and maintain new contacts and sales leads to achieve set sales targets.</li>\n  <li>Consistently meet or exceed monthly, quarterly, and annual sales quotas.</li>\n  <li>Drive student enrolment numbers through various initiatives such as campaigns, open houses, information sessions, and campus visits.</li>\n  <li>Monitor competitors and industry trends in the education sector to formulate effective sales strategies and initiatives.</li>\n  <li>Take ownership of achieving and surpassing sales targets in alignment with the institution’s core competencies.</li>\n  <li>Ensure full compliance with SSG regulations and strict adherence to the Institute’s policies and procedures.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma or Degree with at least 1 year of relevant experience, preferably within the education industry.</li>\n  <li>Proven track record in sales management is essential.</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with the education market and strong assessment abilities will be an advantage.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd | EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R22110981| EA Personnel Name: Law Mei Fong</p>",
